verbose_text: Osteogenic differentiation was assessed by evaluating alkaline phosphatase (ALP) activity and the mRNA and protein expression of osteogenesis related genes, including ALP, bone morphogenetic protein 2 (BMP2), Runt related transcription factor-2 (Runx-2), osterix, osteopontin (OPN) and osteocalcin.
evidence: expression of osteogenesis-related genes, including ALP, bone morphogenetic protein 2 (BMP2), Runt-related transcription factor-2
